OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5F'The Hajj is my dream but  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FI'm shocked by the cost'   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Some 1.8 million Muslims from across   
OL,6, the world made it to Mount Arafat in   
OL,7, Saudi Arabia on Tuesday to mark the    
OL,8, most important day of the Hajj. But due
OL,9, to global price rises, the pilgrimage  
OL,10, is becoming increasingly unaffordable. 
OL,12,F"The number of bookings has            
OL,13,Fsignificantly dropped this year. It's  
OL,14,Ftoo costly for many people," says an   
OL,15,Femployee at a private Egyptian tour    
OL,16,Foperator in charge of organising Hajj  
OL,17,Ftrips, who wanted to remain anonymous  
OL,18,Fout of fear of a backlash over their   
OL,19,Fcriticism of their country's economic  
OL,20,Fsituation.                             
